# Free Knowledge App

A free, donation-supported knowledge management application with AI assistance, database capabilities, and formula calculations.

## Features

- ✅ Full document editing
- ✅ AI chat assistance
- ✅ Database & relation support
- ✅ Formula calculations
- ✅ Mobile-responsive design
- ✅ API integration
- ✅ Optional donations
- ✅ No paywalls

## Technology Stack

- React + Vite (Frontend)
- Tailwind CSS (Styling)
- JavaScript (Logic)
- Buildin.ai API (Backend integration)

## Installation

1. Clone this repository
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
